<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/74712690-paul-hedeen"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1512667838i/74712690._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/74712690-paul-hedeen">Paul Hedeen</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I took the cave as a symbol and foreshadowing of the likely fates of the Native Americans. That the priest was saved by a Native American in a holy pl<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I took the cave as a symbol and foreshadowing of the likely fates of the Native Americans. That the priest was saved by a Native American in a holy place is really a metaphor for the priest's whole existence in NM. Beneath the surface world is what? The grave is what?<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
