        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2271044395" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14308238973111974619">What can I say about this book? It was beautiful, it was peaceful, it was perfect. A book I will re-read periodically, when I need to leave the world behind.<br/>There is no real plot other than the lives of two French priests who come to Santa Fe in 1850 to create a Catholic mission to serve the Indians and Mexicans. Father LaTour and Father Vaillant will be riding their mules in my head forever, spreading kindness.<br/><br/>Beautiful, peaceful, perfect.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


